import React from 'react';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  Grid,
  Paper,
  Typography,
  Box,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  CardActions,
  Button
} from '@mui/material';
import {
  CloudUpload,
  Email,
  Share,
  Schedule,
  Group,
  Campaign
} from '@mui/icons-material';

function Dashboard() {
  const navigate = useNavigate();

  const features = [
    {
      title: 'File Upload',
      description: 'Upload videos, images, and documents',
      icon: <CloudUpload sx={{ fontSize: 48 }} />,
      path: '/upload',
      color: '#2196f3'
    },
    {
      title: 'Recipients',
      description: 'Manage email and phone contacts',
      icon: <Group sx={{ fontSize: 48 }} />,
      path: '/recipients',
      color: '#4caf50'
    },
    {
      title: 'Send Now',
      description: 'Distribute files immediately',
      icon: <Email sx={{ fontSize: 48 }} />,
      path: '/schedule',
      color: '#ff9800'
    },
    {
      title: 'Schedule',
      description: 'Schedule automated distributions',
      icon: <Schedule sx={{ fontSize: 48 }} />,
      path: '/schedule',
      color: '#9c27b0'
    },
    {
      title: 'Social Media',
      description: 'Post to multiple platforms',
      icon: <Share sx={{ fontSize: 48 }} />,
      path: '/schedule',
      color: '#f44336'
    },
    {
      title: 'Campaigns',
      description: 'Create multi-channel campaigns',
      icon: <Campaign sx={{ fontSize: 48 }} />,
      path: '/campaigns',
      color: '#00bcd4'
    }
  ];

  return (
    <Box sx={{ p: 3 }}>
      <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
        File Distribution Dashboard
      </Typography>
      <Typography variant="body1" color="textSecondary" sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
        Automate sending files via email, social media, and iMessage
      </Typography>

      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        {features.map((feature, index) => (
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} key={index}>
            <Card
              sx={{
                height: '100%',
                display: 'flex',
                flexDirection: 'column',
                transition: 'transform 0.2s',
                '&:hover': {
                  transform: 'translateY(-4px)',
                  boxShadow: 3
                }
              }}
            >
              <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1, textAlign: 'center' }}>
                <Box sx={{ color: feature.color, mb: 2 }}>
                  {feature.icon}
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="h6" component="h2" gutterBottom>
                  {feature.title}
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                  {feature.description}
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
              <CardActions>
                <Button
                  fullWidth
                  variant="contained"
                  onClick={() => navigate(feature.path)}
                  sx={{ backgroundColor: feature.color }}
                >
                  Open
                </Button>
              </CardActions>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        ))}
      </Grid>

      <Paper sx={{ p: 3, mt: 4 }}>
        <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
          Quick Stats
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={3}>
            <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Typography variant="h4" color="primary">0</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                Files Uploaded
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={3}>
            <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Typography variant="h4" color="primary">0</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                Recipients
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={3}>
            <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Typography variant="h4" color="primary">0</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                Scheduled Tasks
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={3}>
            <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Typography variant="h4" color="primary">0</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                Active Campaigns
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Paper>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Dashboard;
